- Per-job budget decrements after execution and returns `CancelJob` at zero: [implementation](/Users/aipalm/.local/share/nx01/w/r5af0665ad1be/fa265b8ab039e/A1/repo/schedule/__init__.py:708).
- `run_pending()` and `run_all()` coverage: [tests](/Users/aipalm/.local/share/nx01/w/r5af0665ad1be/fa265b8ab039e/A1/repo/test_schedule.py:405).
